hvib <- hatch %>%
  filter(Genus == "Vibrio")

Present_vibreos <- hvib %>% group_by(Tag_ASV) %>% summarise(totrat = sum(ratio)) %>% filter(totrat > 0) %>% pull(Tag_ASV)
hvib <- hvib %>% filter(Tag_ASV %in% Present_vibreos)
